title: Willie Nile 2013-11-28 Dortmund blu-ray
description:
Willie Nile 2013-11-28 Dortmund blu-ray (2cam mix, dubbed audio)

1080i30, 22mbit cbr, 24/96 PCM audio, BD25 disc
blu-ray has menus and pop-up menus for song selection during playback

Check out this great musician if you don't already know him. It's free leech as of now (don't know how long it will be free leech so grab it now!) and a great quality video.
Sample at:

Willie's music is very special to me. Out of my 1000+ records his album "Streets of New York" is one of my most played ones.

The video is mainly a 2cam mix. I filmed the whole show except three minutes of "House of a thousand guitars" where silly me though I was recording but I was not. My friend recorded that song but thought I was filming the "secure" angle so he was moving the camera around a lot. Still very enjoyable.
Please note: My friend filmed not all of the show but a lot so this is mainly a 2cam mix. Both cameras set to 1080p-50 and for this blu-ray edited to 1080i/30 NTSC for worldwide playback. The lightning was horrible for recording but it's a great club with great sound. Highly recommended. Check out the "Blue Notez" in Dortmund if you are looking for a nice concert setting.
Audio source: CA14 cards - CA ugly II pre-amp - Tascam DR-2d @ 24/96
